cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY 

This paper deals with the categorization of Bangla web documents using machine learning approaches. This task falls under the sub-categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, since the paper deals with a specific language, Bangla, it could also be categorized under computational linguistics (cs.CY).
